===Pronunciation===
* {{IPA|/pəˈdʒɑ.məz/|/pəˈdʒæ.məz/|lang=en}}
* {{audio|en-us-pajamas.ogg|Audio (US)|lang=en}}

===Noun===
{{wikipedia}}
{{en-plural noun|sg=pajama}}

# [[clothes|Clothes]] for wearing to bed and sleeping in, usually consisting of a loose-fitting shirt and pants/trousers.
# Loose-fitting [[trousers]] worn by both sexes in various southern Asian countries including [[India]].

